  • Deprecated Classes 
    Class and Description
    org.springframework.format.number.CurrencyFormatter
    as of Spring 4.2, in favor of the more clearly named CurrencyStyleFormatter
    org.springframework.cache.interceptor.DefaultKeyGenerator
    as of Spring 4.0, in favor of SimpleKeyGenerator or custom KeyGenerator implementations based on hash codes
    org.springframework.scripting.jruby.JRubyScriptFactory
    in favor of JRuby support via the JSR-223 abstraction (StandardScriptFactory)
    org.springframework.scripting.jruby.JRubyScriptUtils
    in favor of JRuby support via the JSR-223 abstraction (StandardScriptFactory)
    org.springframework.format.number.NumberFormatter
    as of Spring 4.2, in favor of the more clearly named NumberStyleFormatter
    org.springframework.format.number.PercentFormatter
    as of Spring 4.2, in favor of the more clearly named PercentStyleFormatter

    since Spring 3.2, in favor of RegistrationPolicy.IGNORE_EXISTING
    org.springframework.jmx.support.MBeanRegistrationSupport.REGISTRATION_REPLACE_EXISTING

  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description

    as of Spring 4.3, in favor of AbstractCacheManager.getMissingCache(String)

    as of Spring 4.0, since Java 6 is required anyway now
    org.springframework.context.support.PropertySourcesPlaceholderConfigurer.processProperties(ConfigurableListableBeanFactory, Properties)
    in favor of PropertySourcesPlaceholderConfigurer.processProperties(ConfigurableListableBeanFactory, ConfigurablePropertyResolver)

    as of 4.3, in favor of CacheAspectSupport.setBeanFactory(org.springframework.beans.factory.BeanFactory)
    org.springframework.validation.DataBinder.setExtractOldValueForEditor(boolean)
    as of Spring 4.3.5, in favor of customizing this in DataBinder.createBeanPropertyBindingResult() or DataBinder.createDirectFieldBindingResult() itself
    org.springframework.jmx.support.MBeanRegistrationSupport.setRegistrationBehavior(int)
    since Spring 3.2, in favor of MBeanRegistrationSupport.setRegistrationPolicy(RegistrationPolicy)
    org.springframework.jmx.support.MBeanRegistrationSupport.setRegistrationBehaviorName(String)
    since Spring 3.2, in favor of MBeanRegistrationSupport.setRegistrationPolicy(RegistrationPolicy)
